<c74object name='av.pix.pong' category='' module=''>

    <digest>
        Range limit (fold, wrap, clip) a texture
    </digest>

    <description>
        Various range limiting modes for textures, such as fold, wrap and clip. Similar to pong/pong~ in event and signal domain. Preserves the alpha channel (doesn't wrap/fold/clip it). Works best when using floating-point types such as float16 or float32.<br/><br/>

The range limiting modes:
mode 0: fold <br/>
mode 1: wrap <br/>
mode 2: clip <br/>
mode 3: none <br/>

    </description>
    
    <discussion>
        
    </discussion>

